OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,FIran begin their World Cup campaign on
OL,8,FMonday in Los Angeles on Monday in
OL,9,Ftheir opening match against New
OL,10,FZealand amid what the team described
OL,11,Fas an uncomfortable "tension".
OL,13,FDespite a tentative peace deal between
OL,14,FTehran and Washington, Team Melli said
OL,15,Fany joy from their World Cup
OL,16,Fexperience has been marred by the
OL,17,Fdisruption and uncertainty they faced
OL,18,Fbefore even arriving on US soil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
