PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,FAgainst the backdrop of war with the
OL,8,FUS and Israel, the squad's training
OL,9,Fbase was moved from Tucson, Arizona,
OL,10,Fto Tijuana, Mexico, after Washington
OL,11,Fdeclined to host the squad for the
OL,12,Ftournament because of uncertainty and
OL,13,Fwider security concerns.
OL,15,FJust days before the World Cup opening
OL,16,Fceremony, the Iranian federation
OL,17,Fclaimed in a statement reported by
OL,18,Fsemi-official state media that it was
OL,19,Fnow unable to provide any tickets to
OL,20,Fits supporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
