PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,FDuring Friday's opening ceremony in
OL,8,FLos Angeles, members of the mostly
OL,9,FAmerican crowd booed when Iran's flag
OL,10,Fwas brought onto the field.
OL,12,FIf the United States and Iran both
OL,13,Fcome out of their groups in second
OL,14,Fplace, they will meet each other in
OL,15,Fthe round of 32, which could further
OL,16,Fadd to tensions felt among fans and
OL,17,Fplayers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
