PN,31404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,FMeanwhile, the United States' sizeable
OL,8,FIranian diaspora remains torn over
OL,9,Ftheir native country's participation
OL,10,Fin this year's tournament, with some
OL,11,Fset to attend a protest outside Los
OL,12,FAngeles stadium while others plan to
OL,13,Fthrow watch parties.
OL,15,FThe Iranian team arrived in the Los
OL,16,FAngeles area on Sunday from their
OL,17,Ftraining base in Tijuana ` about 140
OL,18,Fmiles from the 70,000-seat Los Angeles
OL,19,FRams' stadium, where they will open
OL,20,Ftheir group-stage play against New
OL,21,FZealand at 2am UK time.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
