OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,FSpeaking at a press conference ahead
OL,8,Fof the match, Iran's captain Mehdi
OL,9,FTaremi said: "I have felt the tension
OL,10,Ffrom the first moment we arrived at
OL,11,Fthis World Cup.
OL,13,F"At any tournament, when there is
OL,14,Ftension, we won't have the same
OL,15,Fbeautiful experience we always talk
OL,16,Fabout with peace and joy.
OL,26,@qD@NOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
