PN,31406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,F"I know it wasn't just us. I know
OL,8,Fseveral countries had visa problems
OL,9,Fand changes with training camps," said
OL,10,Fthe 33-year-old Olympiacos striker,
OL,11,Fwho is playing in his third World Cup.
OL,13,F"This kind of tension, it undermines
OL,14,Fthat joy and it undermines the message
OL,15,Fof FIFA and our people, which is that
OL,16,Ffootball brings about peace."
OL,18,FTaremi insisted his side plays "for
OL,19,Fevery Iranian, be it in the diaspora
OL,20,For in Iran".
