CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781581669
OL,3,CIran prepares for World Cup opener
OL,4,Camid interim peace deal and protests
OL,5,Cin LA
OL,7,F"People have different opinions, but
OL,8,Fwe are here to unite people and we
OL,9,Fwill try to bring joy to all Iranians
OL,10,Fwherever they live," he said.
OL,12,FIran coach Amir Ghalenoei added: "I am
OL,13,Fjust happy that they are coming to
OL,14,Fwatch us and I hope that they will
OL,15,Fpray for us and I hope that they will
OL,16,Fencourage us."
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@TO]tD@bOUxD@NO]
